  <h1>Ghost - Vehicle Protection</h1>
  <img src="/files/ghost-protection.jpg" class="highlight_image_big" alt="Ghost Vehicle Protection" />
  <p>With thieves becoming more sophisticated and determined using relay devices, hacking your car, key cloning or worst of all breaking into your home and hijacking you for the keys, modern cars are actually more vulnerable than ever from theft. We can protect your vehicle with the Ghost immobiliser which has been specifically designed for modern vehicles to stop your vehicle from being stolen in any of these ways.</p>
  <p>The only way a thief could take a Ghost protected car is by physically towing it away — even then they will never be able to drive it! The Ghost has no key-fobs or LED indications to give away its location. The Ghost uses the buttons in your vehicle such as those on the steering wheel, door panels or centre console, to allow you to make a unique, changeable, PIN code sequence that must first be entered before you can drive your car. Just like your credit card but you can make your car PIN even safer by making it up to 20 presses long!</p>
  <p>In order to make extreme security also be hassle free, there is even an iPhone application that connects to your car and allows you to get in and drive without having to enter the PIN code. This iPhone pairing allows a single, authorised, connection with a secret pairing code that is unique to every Ghost and communication between the Ghost and the iPhone is encrypted. All you have to do is pair your iPhone with your Ghost, leave the Autowatch Ghost application running in the background with Bluetooth enabled and you can drive conveniently and securely.</p>
  <p>This system really is a car saver — we have had multiple customers who have had the misfortune of an attempted theft report that the Ghost system fitted by ourselves has saved their car from being taken.</p>
